Definition: a remark that calls attention to something or someone
Example: she made frequent mention of her promotion; there was no mention of it; the speaker made several references to his wife
Synonyms: verb, communication, reference, refer, remark, a, that, calls, attention, to, something, or, someone, she, made, frequent, of, her, promotion, there, was, no, it, the, speaker, several, references, his, wife
Category: noun.communication
